"the dimension of infinite consciousness beset me, and that was an affliction "
"for me."

msgctxt "an9.41:13.15"
msgid "Seyyathāpi, ānanda, sukhino dukkhaṃ uppajjeyya yāvadeva ābādhāya;"
msgstr ""
"Suppose a happy person were to experience pain; that would be an affliction "
"for them."

msgctxt "an9.41:13.16"
msgid ""
"evamevassa me viññāṇañcāyatanasahagatā saññāmanasikārā samudācaranti. Svassa "
"me hoti ābādho."
msgstr ""
"In the same way, when perceptions and attentions accompanied by the "
"dimension of infinite consciousness beset me, that was an affliction for me."

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="pts-vp-pi" id="pts-vp-pi4.447"></a>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc14"></a>
msgctxt "an9.41:14.1"
msgid "Tassa mayhaṃ, ānanda, etadahosi:"
msgstr "Then I thought:"

msgctxt "an9.41:14.2"
msgid ""
"‘yannūnāhaṃ sabbaso ākiñcaññāyatanaṃ samatikkamma nevasaññānāsaññāyatanaṃ "
"upasampajja vihareyyan’ti."
msgstr ""
"‘Why don’t I, going totally beyond the dimension of nothingness, enter and "
"remain in the dimension of neither perception nor non-perception?’"

msgctxt "an9.41:14.3"
msgid ""
"Tassa mayhaṃ, ānanda, nevasaññānāsaññāyatane cittaṃ na pakkhandati "
"nappasīdati na santiṭṭhati na vimuccati etaṃ santanti passato."
msgstr ""
"But my mind wasn’t eager for the dimension of neither perception nor non-"
"perception; it wasn’t confident, settled, and decided about it. I didn’t see "
"it as peaceful."

msgctxt "an9.41:14.4"
msgid "Tassa mayhaṃ, ānanda, etadahosi:"
msgstr "Then I thought:"

msgctxt "an9.41:14.5"
msgid ""
"‘ko nu kho hetu ko paccayo, yena me nevasaññānāsaññāyatane cittaṃ na "
"pakkhandati nappasīdati na santiṭṭhati na vimuccati etaṃ santanti passato’?"
msgstr ""
"‘What is the cause, what is the reason why my mind isn’t eager for the "
"dimension of neither perception nor non-perception, and not confident, "
"settled, and decided about it? Why don’t I see it as peaceful?’"

msgctxt "an9.41:14.6"
msgid "Tassa mayhaṃ, ānanda, etadahosi:"
msgstr "Then I thought:"

msgctxt "an9.41:14.7"
msgid ""
"‘ākiñcaññāyatane kho me ādīnavo adiṭṭho, so ca me abahulīkato, "
"nevasaññānāsaññāyatane ca ānisaṃso anadhigato, so ca me anāsevito."
msgstr ""
"‘I haven’t seen the drawbacks of the dimension of nothingness, and so I "
"haven’t cultivated that. I haven’t realized the benefits of the dimension of "
"neither perception nor non-perception, and so I haven’t developed that."

msgctxt "an9.41:14.8"
msgid ""
"Tasmā me nevasaññānāsaññāyatane cittaṃ na pakkhandati nappasīdati na "
"santiṭṭhati na vimuccati etaṃ santanti passato’."
msgstr ""
"That’s why my mind isn’t eager for the dimension of neither perception nor "
"non-perception, and not confident, settled, and decided about it. And it’s "
"why I don’t see it as peaceful.’"

msgctxt "an9.41:14.9"
msgid "Tassa mayhaṃ, ānanda, etadahosi:"
msgstr "Then I thought:"

msgctxt "an9.41:14.10"
msgid ""
"‘sace kho ahaṃ ākiñcaññāyatane ādīnavaṃ disvā taṃ bahulaṃ kareyyaṃ, "
"nevasaññānāsaññāyatane ānisaṃsaṃ adhigamma tamāseveyyaṃ, ṭhānaṃ kho panetaṃ "
"vijjati yaṃ me nevasaññānāsaññāyatane cittaṃ pakkhandeyya pasīdeyya "
"santiṭṭheyya vimucceyya etaṃ santanti passato’."
msgstr ""
"‘Suppose that, seeing the drawbacks of the dimension of nothingness, I was "
"to cultivate that. And suppose that, realizing the benefits of the dimension "
"of neither perception nor non-perception, I was to develop that. It’s "
"possible that my mind would be eager to be free from the dimension of "
"nothingness; it would be confident, settled, and decided about it. And I "
"would see it as peaceful.’"

msgctxt "an9.41:14.11"
msgid ""
"So kho ahaṃ, ānanda, aparena samayena ākiñcaññāyatane ādīnavaṃ disvā taṃ "
"bahulamakāsiṃ, nevasaññānāsaññāyatane ānisaṃsaṃ adhigamma tamāseviṃ."
msgstr ""
"And so, after some time, I saw the drawbacks of the dimension of nothingness "
"and cultivated that, and I realized the benefits of the dimension of neither "
"perception nor non-perception and developed that."

msgctxt "an9.41:14.12"
msgid ""
"Tassa mayhaṃ, ānanda, nevasaññānāsaññāyatane cittaṃ pakkhandati pasīdati "
"santiṭṭhati vimuccati etaṃ santanti passato."
msgstr ""
"Then my mind was eager for the dimension of neither perception nor non-"
"perception; it was confident, settled, and decided about it. I saw it as "
"peaceful."

msgctxt "an9.41:14.13"
msgid ""
"So kho ahaṃ, ānanda, sabbaso ākiñcaññāyatanaṃ samatikkamma "
"nevasaññānāsaññāyatanaṃ upasampajja viharāmi."
msgstr ""
"And so, going totally beyond the dimension of nothingness, I was entering "
"and remaining in the dimension of neither perception nor non-perception."

msgctxt "an9.41:14.14"
msgid ""
"Tassa mayhaṃ, ānanda, iminā vihārena viharato ākiñcaññāyatanasahagatā "
"saññāmanasikārā samudācaranti. Svassa me hoti ābādho."
msgstr ""
"While I was in that meditation, perceptions and attentions accompanied by "
"the dimension of nothingness beset me, and that was an affliction for me."

msgctxt "an9.41:14.15"
msgid "Seyyathāpi, ānanda, sukhino dukkhaṃ uppajjeyya yāvadeva ābādhāya;"
msgstr ""
"Suppose a happy person were to experience pain; that would be an affliction "
"for them."

msgctxt "an9.41:14.16"
msgid ""
"evamevassa me ākiñcaññāyatanasahagatā saññāmanasikārā samudācaranti. Svassa "
"me hoti ābādho."
msgstr ""
"In the same way, when perceptions and attentions accompanied by the "
"dimension of nothingness beset me, that was an affliction for me."

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="pts-vp-pi" id="pts-vp-pi4.448"></a>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc15"></a>
msgctxt "an9.41:15.1"
msgid "Tassa mayhaṃ, ānanda, etadahosi:"
msgstr "Then I thought:"

msgctxt "an9.41:15.2"
msgid ""
"‘yannūnāhaṃ nevasaññānāsaññāyatanaṃ samatikkamma saññāvedayitanirodhaṃ "
"upasampajja vihareyyan’ti."
msgstr ""
"‘Why don’t I, going totally beyond the dimension of neither perception nor "
"non-perception, enter and remain in the cessation of perception and feeling?’"

msgctxt "an9.41:15.3"
msgid ""
"Tassa mayhaṃ, ānanda, saññāvedayitanirodhe cittaṃ na pakkhandati nappasīdati "
"na santiṭṭhati na vimuccati etaṃ santanti passato."
msgstr ""
"But my mind wasn’t eager for the cessation of perception and feeling; it "
"wasn’t confident, settled, and decided about it. I didn’t see it as peaceful."

msgctxt "an9.41:15.4"
msgid "Tassa mayhaṃ, ānanda, etadahosi:"
msgstr "Then I thought:"

msgctxt "an9.41:15.5"
msgid ""
"‘ko nu kho hetu, ko paccayo, yena me saññāvedayitanirodhe cittaṃ na "
"pakkhandati nappasīdati na santiṭṭhati na vimuccati etaṃ santanti passato’?"
msgstr ""
"‘What is the cause, what is the reason why my mind isn’t eager for the "
"cessation of perception and feeling, and not confident, settled, and decided "
"about it? Why don’t I see it as peaceful?’"

msgctxt "an9.41:15.6"
msgid "Tassa mayhaṃ, ānanda, etadahosi:"
msgstr "Then I thought:"

msgctxt "an9.41:15.7"
msgid ""
"‘nevasaññānāsaññāyatane kho me ādīnavo adiṭṭho, so ca me abahulīkato, "
"saññāvedayitanirodhe ca ānisaṃso anadhigato, so ca me anāsevito."
msgstr ""
"‘I haven’t seen the drawbacks of the dimension of neither perception nor non-"
"perception, and so I haven’t cultivated that. I haven’t realized the "
"benefits of the cessation of perception and feeling, and so I haven’t "
"developed that."

msgctxt "an9.41:15.8"
msgid ""
"Tasmā me saññāvedayitanirodhe cittaṃ na pakkhandati nappasīdati na "
"santiṭṭhati na vimuccati etaṃ santanti passato’."
msgstr ""
"That’s why my mind isn’t eager for the cessation of perception and feeling, "
"and not confident, settled, and decided about it. And it’s why I don’t see "
"it as peaceful.’"

msgctxt "an9.41:15.9"
msgid "Tassa mayhaṃ, ānanda, etadahosi:"
msgstr "Then I thought:"

msgctxt "an9.41:15.10"
msgid ""
"‘sace kho ahaṃ nevasaññānāsaññāyatane ādīnavaṃ disvā taṃ bahulaṃ kareyyaṃ, "
"saññāvedayitanirodhe ānisaṃsaṃ adhigamma tamāseveyyaṃ, ṭhānaṃ kho panetaṃ "
"vijjati yaṃ me saññāvedayitanirodhe cittaṃ pakkhandeyya pasīdeyya "
"santiṭṭheyya vimucceyya etaṃ santanti passato’."
msgstr ""
"‘Suppose that, seeing the drawbacks of the dimension of neither perception "
"nor non-perception, I was to cultivate that. And suppose that, realizing the "
"benefits of the cessation of perception and feeling, I was to develop that. "
"It’s possible that my mind would be eager to be free from the dimension of "
"neither perception nor non-perception; it would be confident, settled, and "
"decided about it. And I would see it as peaceful.’"

msgctxt "an9.41:15.11"
msgid ""
"So kho ahaṃ, ānanda, aparena samayena nevasaññānāsaññāyatane ādīnavaṃ disvā "
"taṃ bahulamakāsiṃ, saññāvedayitanirodhe ānisaṃsaṃ adhigamma tamāseviṃ."
msgstr ""
"And so, after some time, I saw the drawbacks of the dimension of neither "
"perception nor non-perception and cultivated that, and I realized the "
"benefits of the cessation of perception and feeling and developed that."

msgctxt "an9.41:15.12"
msgid ""
"Tassa mayhaṃ, ānanda, saññāvedayitanirodhe cittaṃ pakkhandati pasīdati "
"santiṭṭhati vimuccati etaṃ santanti passato."
msgstr ""
"Then my mind was eager for the cessation of perception and feeling; it was "
"confident, settled, and decided about it. I saw it as peaceful."

msgctxt "an9.41:15.13"
msgid ""
"So kho ahaṃ, ānanda, sabbaso nevasaññānāsaññāyatanaṃ samatikkamma "
"saññāvedayitanirodhaṃ upasampajja viharāmi, paññāya ca me disvā āsavā "
"parikkhayaṃ agamaṃsu."
msgstr ""
"And so, going totally beyond the dimension of neither perception nor non-"
"perception, I was entering and remaining in the cessation of perception and "
"feeling. And, having seen with wisdom, my defilements were ended."

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc16"></a>
msgctxt "an9.41:16.1"
msgid ""
"Yāvakīvañcāhaṃ, ānanda, imā nava anupubbavihārasamāpattiyo na evaṃ "
"anulomapaṭilomaṃ samāpajjimpi vuṭṭhahimpi, neva tāvāhaṃ, ānanda, sadevake "
"loke samārake sabrahmake sassamaṇabrāhmaṇiyā pajāya sadevamanussāya ‘"
"anuttaraṃ sammāsambodhiṃ abhisambuddho’ti paccaññāsiṃ."
msgstr ""
"As long as I hadn’t entered into and withdrawn from these nine progressive "
"meditative attainments in both forward and reverse order, I didn’t announce "
"my supreme perfect awakening in this world with its gods, Māras, and "
"Brahmās, this population with its ascetics and brahmins, its gods and humans."

msgctxt "an9.41:16.2"
msgid ""
"Yato ca kho ahaṃ, ānanda, imā nava anupubbavihārasamāpattiyo evaṃ "
"anulomapaṭilomaṃ samāpajjimpi vuṭṭhahimpi, athāhaṃ, ānanda, sadevake loke "
"samārake sabrahmake sassamaṇabrāhmaṇiyā pajāya sadevamanussāya ‘anuttaraṃ "
"sammāsambodhiṃ abhisambuddho’ti paccaññāsiṃ."
msgstr ""
"But when I had entered into and withdrawn from these nine progressive "
"meditative attainments in both forward and reverse order, I announced my "
"supreme perfect awakening in this world with its gods, Māras, and Brahmās, "
"this population with its ascetics and brahmins, its gods and humans."

msgctxt "an9.41:16.3"
msgid "Ñāṇañca pana me dassanaṃ udapādi: "
msgstr "Knowledge and vision arose in me: "

#. VAR: cetovimutti → vimutti (si, mr)
msgctxt "an9.41:16.4"
msgid "‘akuppā me cetovimutti, ayamantimā jāti, natthi dāni punabbhavo’”ti."
msgstr ""
"‘My freedom is unshakable; this is my last rebirth; now there are no more "
"future lives.’”"

#. </p><p class="endsection">
msgctxt "an9.41:16.5"
msgid "Dasamaṃ."
msgstr ""

#. </p><p class="endsection">
msgctxt "an9.41:16.6"
msgid "Mahāvaggo catuttho."
msgstr ""

#. </p><blockquote class="uddanagatha"><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc17"></a>
msgctxt "an9.41:17.1"
msgid "Dve vihārā ca nibbānaṃ,"
msgstr ""

#. <br>
msgctxt "an9.41:17.2"
msgid "gāvī jhānena pañcamaṃ;"
msgstr ""

#. <br>
msgctxt "an9.41:17.3"
msgid "Ānando brāhmaṇā devo,"
msgstr ""

#. <br>
msgctxt "an9.41:17.4"
msgid "nāgena tapussena cāti."
msgstr ""
